item.title: CVE-2021-24553|2024-08-03T19:35:20.133Z -- unknown -- timeline%20calendar
item.description: The Timeline Calendar WordPress plugin through 1.2 does not sanitise, validate or escape the edit GET parameter before using it in a SQL statement when editing events, leading to an authenticated SQL injection issue. Other SQL Injections are also present in the plugin
